data.description: Check out all the charm and character this three-bedroom, three-bath home has to offer! Walk into a large kitchen with hardwood floors, lots of storage, a center island and a vaulted ceiling making it a light and bright space. A large dining room with bay windows looking out to the deck, den, one-half bath and living room are also located on the main floor. Upstairs are three bedrooms (primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet) plus a full bath. In the basement there is lots of storage space, a utility room, full bath, laundry area, exercise room with sauna plus a family room. Outside, there is a detached one-car garage which is insulated and heated along with a very handy covered car port plus a large deck to enjoy the river valley view. Partially fenced yard. This home has lots of beautiful natural woodwork. Schedule your showing soon!
